ton）。<br />\n最有機三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc4ce80ea758a441417b913b02407053701c6ae","tid":506958,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:08:24.000Z","msg":"遲早入晒，有乜好爭"},{"pid":"21e890645b221b04154eb579b30eb548438a678e","tid":506958,"uid":46507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:55:15.000Z","msg":"nash <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590fb5e8d2921fd0ee206600a40b324d8b33df84","tid":506958,"uid":131423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:38:42.000Z","msg":"三月都一定入到<br />\nNash 2次mvp都已經保送佢入去<br />\nRay Allen 係三分代言人，三分record都夠佢入啦<br />\nJason Kidd 三雙、助攻都夠玩<br />\n最重要嘅係佢三個都係劃時代嘅球員、打法同實力改變左個聯盟生態，一早就話佢地係future hall of flamer"},{"pid":"c03966a3a1d6c8c4bf9533aa8aaabcdfc6b6db6a","tid":506958,"uid":131423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"590fb5e8d2921fd0ee206600a40b324d8b33df84","tid":506958,"uid":131423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:38:42.000Z","msg":"三月都一定入到<br />\nNash 2次mvp都已經保送佢入去<br />\nRay Allen 係三分代言人，三分record都夠佢入啦<br />\nJason Kidd 三雙、助攻都夠玩<br />\n最重要嘅係佢三個都係劃時代嘅球員、打法同實力改變左個聯盟生態，一早就話佢地係future hall of flamer"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:38:59.000Z","msg":"三個"}]}